Subject: [PATCH] fix: correct pipe shuffle math + fix buttons not working
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- IntroLoader: start with sSali (mathematically verified) → 4 rotations → Salis
- page.tsx: replace pointerEvents:none with visibility:hidden
  so CartDrawer and CheckoutModal always receive pointer events
- Navbar renders only after introComplete to avoid layout shift
